lead_paragraph: Arsenal midfielder Santi Cazorla has returned to fitness after a five-month injury layoff, handing manager Arsene Wenger a late-season boost before Sunday's away clash with Manchester City.

headline.print_headline: Cazorla Hands Wenger Fitness Boost Before Man City Trip
